515
00:29:37.729 --> 00:29:39.630
Jangan berpikiran terlalu jauh.

516
00:29:40.130 --> 00:29:41.999
Aku mengakui kesalahan kata-kataku.

517
00:29:42.539 --> 00:29:45.239
